  <text>
    <front>
      <div type="printedheader">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7796_p1"> <seg type="com">
                        <note type="addendum" xml:id="K_7796_c0">Nachträgliche Notiz oben links von dritter Hand mit Bleistift: <bibl>ad Offerten aller Art.</bibl> </note>
                    </seg> <lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
          <fw>THE PATENT <lb xml:id="p1-l2"/>TUNNELING
        <lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>&amp; MINING MACHINE
        <lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>COMPANY.
        <lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>LIMITED</fw>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="address">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7796_p2">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l6"/>
          <fw>18. Finsbury Circus.</fw>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_7796_p3">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>
          <fw>
            <placeName type="place" key="London (UK)">London</placeName>
            <choice>
                            <abbr>E. C.</abbr>
                            <expan>Eastern Central (östlicher Stadtteil)</expan>
                        </choice>
                    </fw>, <date when="1872-06-27">27<hi rend="sup">t</hi> June <fw>187</fw>2</date> </p>
      </div>
      <div type="address">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7796_p4">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>From <choice>
                        <abbr>Lt: Colonel</abbr>
                        <expan>Lieutenant Colonel (Oberstleutnant)</expan>
                    </choice> Holland
        <lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>President
        <lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>of the Patent Tunneling &amp; Mining Machine <choice>
                        <abbr>C<hi rend="sup">o</hi> </abbr>
                        <expan>Compagnia / Compagnie / Company (Gesellschaft)</expan>
                    </choice> <choice>
                        <abbr>Ltd</abbr>
                        <expan>[with] Limited [liability] (mit beschränkter Haftung)</expan>
                    </choice> </p>
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7796_p5">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>To
        <lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>
                    <choice>
                        <abbr>Mons:</abbr>
                        <expan>Monsieur (Herr)</expan>
                    </choice> Le President
        <lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>of the <choice>
                        <abbr>St.</abbr>
                        <expan>Sankt / Sanct / Saint (heilig)</expan>
                    </choice> Gothard Railway Company
        <lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>Bellevue
        <lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>
                    <placeName type="place" key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurich</placeName> <lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>Suisse</p>
      </div>
      <div type="opener">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_7796_p6">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>Sir</p>
      </div>
    </front>
    <body>
            <div>
      <p rend="indent" xml:id="K_7796_p7">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>With reference to the Tender sent in by this Company
        <lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>on <date when="1872-06-15">15. <choice>
                            <abbr>ult<hi rend="sup">o</hi> </abbr>
                            <expan>ultimo (letzten [Monats])</expan>
                        </choice>
                    </date> for boring the <placeName type="place" key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">St. Gothard</placeName> Tunnel I write to
        <lb xml:id="p1-l20"/>state that in the event of your requiring Boring Machines
        <lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>to be tested in Switzerland or elsewhere prior to the
        <lb xml:id="p1-l22"/>final acceptance of any Tender, my Company will be
        <lb xml:id="p1-l23"/>happy to send their Machine to any place you may
        <lb xml:id="p1-l24"/>name to test its capabilities on receiving from you
        <lb xml:id="p1-l25"/>or your Engineer-in-Chief an intimation that such is
        <lb xml:id="p1-l26"/>required.</p>
    </div>
        </body>
    <back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_7796_p8">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l27"/>I am, Sir
        <lb xml:id="p1-l28"/>Your most <choice>
                        <abbr>obed<hi rend="sup">t</hi> </abbr>
                        <expan>obedient (ergeben)</expan>
                    </choice> servant</p>
      </div>
      <div type="address">
        <p rend="center" xml:id="K_7796_p9">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l29"/>Trev. Holland.
        <lb xml:id="p1-l30"/>
        <choice>
                        <abbr>Lt: Colonel</abbr>
                        <expan>Lieutenant Colonel (Oberstleutnant)</expan>
                    </choice>
        <lb xml:id="p1-l31"/>President</p> </div>
    </back>
